ElementValueAnnotation, ElementValueArray, ElementValueClass, ElementValueEnum, ElementValuePrimitive
public abstract class ElementValue
extends ClassFileStructure

Representation of a element_value structure of an annotation attribute of a class. This is the abstract class inherited by any type of element_value.

Version:
1.0.0, 2010-06-05

Constructor Detail

ElementValue

protected ElementValue(ClassFile classFile,
                       char tag)
Basic constructor. It is protected since it should be only used by inheriting classes. The appropriate way to initialize a class representing an element_value is to use getElementValue(ClassFile).

Parameters:
classFile - The ClassFile the element_value belongs to.
tag - The tag of this element_value.
